textAnnotations.description:
RIDGID RoboHammer®
RoboHammer® is a more accurate hammer,
with a contoured, non-slip grip that aligns the head
for more consistent hits. Surrounding a one-piece,
solid steel shaft, the triple-layer grip dampens
vibration and reduces fatigue. RoboHammer® is
also the first and only hammer with custom right
and left-handed grips. The superior comfort of this
hammer allows the user to swing harder and with
more confidence.
See more...
